{
  "chapter": 83,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲与徐子陵在九江谋划刺杀任少名。牛方才提供九江城形势图和巡逻时间表，三人商讨潜入春在楼行刺的方案——利用水道潜行破闸、树顶借力索快速移动。寇仲设计高空弹力索系统，牛方才负责制作。二人在酒楼观察地形后沿街行走，发现被青衣人跟踪，将其截住后发现是女扮男装的宋玉致。宋玉致怒斥二人暴露刺杀计划破坏了原有部署，寇仲趁机以赌约求婚被拒。关键时刻徐子陵从河道垂钓者处发现钓鱼丝可替代借力索，寇仲大喜。宋玉致劝二人出城未果，提及杨公宝库的利害关系，最终无奈放任二人赴死。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "speaker_name": "牛方才",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九江处于南北方交通的中心，由南往北的旅人，多从水路乘船至此舍舟登陆，取道北上，故城北的石码头有南船北马之誉，非常兴旺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今趟林士宏和任少名大事张扬在九江结盟的事，正是含有同时向南北诸雄展示实力之意。唉！争天下真非简单的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "speaker_name": "牛方才",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九江南连洞庭，北系大江，水道纵横贯穿，主要部分是旧城区，城墙高十五丈，设四座城门和参道水门。我这兴发隆和春在楼都是在旧城区内，只不过一南一北，分处北门大街和南门大街之端，而两条大街则被位于城心的院署'镇江楼'分隔了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十五丈那么高的墙，得靠勾索一类的辅助工具才可攀过去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "或者可考虑从水道溜走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "speaker_name": "牛方才",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "水道口有双重的钢闸，非常牢固。兼且参个水道口均特别设有监察的岗哨和定时有人巡逻，想预先破坏亦难以实行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "text": "牛叔知否城军巡逻的时间和岗哨更换的时刻呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "speaker_name": "牛方才",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这正是我们的主要工作，全部有纪录，他们共有十个不同时间表，每五日换一次，周而复始。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要我们准确掌握更班和巡逻的时间来进行刺杀行动，便可在敌人发现前，破闸而出，但这当然须有特别的工具了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "speaker_name": "牛方才",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "但那定会惊动哨岗的守卫的。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "text": "那就顺手干掉他们好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "speaker_name": "牛方才",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "哨岗在城墙之上，若能到达那，不如翻墙逃走好了。可是城墙和最接近的房子最少也有二十丈的距离，两位公子若现身在这围内，立即会给发觉，只要他们居高临下向两位放箭，已极难应付。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个倒不成问题，我们可长时间在水底不用换气，就索性由水道潜过去，在水底破闸而出好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "speaker_name": "牛方才",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "若两位确有这种通天的潜水能耐，确是可行之计，因为敌人怎都想不到你们可长时间藏在水内。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "speaker_name": "牛方才",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但最大的问题是根本不可能接近任少名所在的春园而不被发觉。这当然是假定任少名今晚会到那去找霍琪哩！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们就在他赴春在楼途中下手好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "speaker_name": "牛方才",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "任少名因残忍好杀，致仇家极多，所以从不采取相同的路线到某一地点去，此法绝难实行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "春在楼外不是有几颗老榕树吗？我们便在树上来个千秋，借力越过那参十丈许的距离，来到香园的瓦背上。唉！不过逃走就非那般容易了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "世上总难有两全其美的事嘛！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假设我们能在这两棵树的树顶处系上一条又又有弹力的索子，逃走时借力弹起，噢！我的天，再假若我们能多布下这么样的几条高空借力索，不是可来去如飞吗？只是唯一要担心就是会给敌人先一步察觉。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "speaker_name": "牛方才",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这确是妙想天开但又切实可行的方法，索子由我想办法，只要两头绑上包了布的铁，又染为黑色，加上远离地面，希望没有人能发现。剩下的问题就是如何可瞒过敌人的耳目去作这些布置，还有就是两位公子能否毫不差的认准落脚点呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_niu_fang_cai",
      "text": "这两个问题由我们去担心好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们先去察看场地，任少名今晚除非不去春在楼，若去了必然没命离开。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们先在街道这边的大树安装一号借力索，到了另一边街的树顶处时，才安装可使我们弹进院内的二号索，如此只需几个起落就可到达春园，走时依循原路离去便成了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们最好能在任少名抵达前，早一步埋伏在春园外，就不用进屋内动手那么麻烦了，且逃起来也易一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "假若杀不死任少名，就是我们死，不成功就不走，明白吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "完全明白。若不立下死志，我们是绝不会成功的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这其实只是我的事，不应把你牵连进去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你怎么忽然婆妈起来了？且成功总是要付出代价的。有挑战自然就有压力，以前你试过这么矛盾吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这将会是我两兄弟一生中最重要的转捩点，倘能成功，立时可把整个南方的形势扭转过来，同时名震天下。唉！但我却知道你对这些根本没有丝毫兴趣，只是为了帮我才甘冒生命之险，你说我能不矛盾吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "只要你一句话，今晚的行动就作罢算了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "一切依计划而行吧！到了明天，一是任少名横死春园附近，一是双龙帮完蛋了。而第参个可能性只能是任少名根本没有出现。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我没有说错吧！那恶公主对你很有意思哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你忘了她约了风湿寒到这来私会吗？她对我的意思就是要宰掉我，故而这意思是不要也罢。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "女人的心是最难捉摸的。或者她和跋小子好，只是想借他来忘记你，但到看见你时，甚么湿湿寒寒都抛到脑后了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你倒懂得代人自我陶醉。咦！似乎有人跟着我们呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你是否说那穿着青衣的小子，在酒楼门外就一直吊着我们。嘿！转左！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有跟来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "这位兄台。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "终找到你这两个不知'死'字怎么写的小子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们还留在这干甚么？无端端闹得全城都知道你们来刺杀任少名，把我们拟好的计划都给破坏了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "不知我们的约定是否还有效呢？宋小姐有否和令尊翁商量过？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "商量过有甚么用？在如今的情况下，谁都没有机会了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "只要约定仍然有效就成了。小姐请立即离城，明早保证会有好消息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你定是疯了，想死的话不若投河自尽算了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "不若再附加一个赌约，假若我在如此艰难的情况下仍能成功，小姐就委身下嫁我寇仲好不？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你的假肚腩碰着了我呢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "小姐尚未答这有关你终身的问题啊！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你这人为何总爱这么纠缠不清的呢？人家不是早告诉你爹已把我许了给人吗？而且我见到你又烦又气，没许人都不会看上你，也不回家照照镜子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "徐子陵！你也要陪他去发疯么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "今晚就是任少名的忌辰，宋小姐请立即离城。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "原来宋小姐移情别恋看上小陵，我寇仲只好宣布退出这场争逐，只求干掉任少名。噢！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你为何不闪避？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "我想看看能否给你刮醒，那以后就不用害单思病了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "回家再说吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我的娘！仲少！钓鱼丝！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们真蠢！这世上还有甚么索子比这娘的钓丝更够弹力和能避人耳目呢？沈婆娘那趟就是用超细钓丝暗算了我们，还是在光天化日之下。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们在说什么？是否真的疯了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "宋小姐请移玉驾到城外，明天便可能得捷报了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不！你们两个立即随我出城。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "原来宋小姐这么关心我们。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当然关心呢！若'杨公宝库'落到任少名和林士宏手内，整个天下都要遭殃。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "原来你对我那么好。算了！现在各走各路，但别忘了协定，否则我和你宋家以后都完没了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你真的要去送死吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那你们就去死吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    }
  ],
